<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="82000000t" end="99200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我回來了!</b></font></p>
<p begin="106600000t" end="116000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>姐姐  姐姐</b></font></p>
<p begin="118500000t" end="144200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>客人好像還沒睡醒的樣子</b></font></p>
<p begin="148900000t" end="154700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>雷姆  雷姆</b></font></p>
<p begin="158900000t" end="190300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>客人怪可憐的  好像小小年紀就痴呆了</b></font></p>
<p begin="284400000t" end="313200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>客人您怎麼了  身體哪裡不舒服嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="315900000t" end="344200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>客人您怎麼了  難道是舊病復發了嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="349500000t" end="360800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>稍微握一下</b></font></p>
<p begin="423200000t" end="437500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>果然是這樣</b></font></p>
<p begin="445300000t" end="475600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我並沒有搞錯</b></font></p>
<p begin="479100000t" end="488300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不對  客人</b></font></p>
<p begin="491000000t" end="510900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我覺得您完全搞錯了</b></font></p>
<p begin="514500000t" end="522600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不對  客人</b></font></p>
<p begin="528000000t" end="544600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>您出生一定就是個錯誤</b></font></p>
<p begin="549900000t" end="582800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>考慮到以後的事  這些話真叫人笑不出來</b></font></p>
<p begin="589900000t" end="607100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不過現在感覺也還不錯</b></font></p>
<p begin="609800000t" end="618300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>姐姐  姐姐</b></font></p>
<p begin="620800000t" end="649100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>客人說不定是被責備後會開心的麻煩人士</b></font></p>
<p begin="652690000t" end="658200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>雷姆  雷姆</b></font></p>
<p begin="660400000t" end="691900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>客人看起來是被痛罵後會興奮的變態人士</b></font></p>
<p begin="696200000t" end="712300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>突然就這麼說  真是抱歉了</b></font></p>
<p begin="719400000t" end="740700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>但是  我相信著你們</b></font></p>
<p begin="756600000t" end="767800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>讓我們好好相處吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="795400000t" end="815300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>還說怎麼吵吵鬧鬧的  然後過來看看</b></font></p>
<p begin="821300000t" end="838500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>昴看起來很有精神  真是太好了</b></font></p>
<p begin="844400000t" end="867800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>直到剛剛為止心情還很複雜</b></font></p>
<p begin="869500000t" end="891400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>但是看見愛蜜莉雅炭後就煙消雲散了</b></font></p>
<p begin="895200000t" end="922900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>愛蜜莉雅炭就是治療我心房的特效藥呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="928900000t" end="950300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>抱歉  我不太明白你在說什麼</b></font></p>
<p begin="956500000t" end="975300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不過早安  看到你沒事真是太好了</b></font></p>
<p begin="978900000t" end="990700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>嗯  早安</b></font></p>
<p begin="1002200000t" end="1025000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那麼就來開始吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="1137100000t" end="1188400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>自分の過去に囚われ迷って</b></font></p>
<p begin="1137100000t" end="1188400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}無法擺脫自己過去的束縛  迷失了前進方向</b></font></p>
<p begin="1188800000t" end="1238500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>そうじゃないよと　言い聞かせて　全てを</b></font></p>
<p begin="1188800000t" end="1238500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}還自欺述說那並不是全部</b></font></p>
<p begin="1238900000t" end="1289400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>自由に操れるかなんて</b></font></p>
<p begin="1238900000t" end="1289400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}不知道這些是否能自由控制</b></font></p>
<p begin="1290200000t" end="1314400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>分からないよと　空は霞んで</b></font></p>
<p begin="1290200000t" end="1314400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}天色為何又如此朦朧</b></font></p>
<p begin="1315200000t" end="1339000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>正解はどこ</b></font></p>
<p begin="1315200000t" end="1339000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}答案又在何處</b></font></p>
<p begin="1340200000t" end="1391500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>僕の手のひらに　残る大事なもの</b></font></p>
<p begin="1340200000t" end="1391500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}雙手還殘留著有什麼很重要的事尚未完成的感覺</b></font></p>
<p begin="1392000000t" end="1440300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>忘れない記憶　何度でも</b></font></p>
<p begin="1392000000t" end="1440300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}這段記憶將塵封於心  永久保存</b></font></p>
<p begin="1440300000t" end="1491600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>君を守り抜くと叫んで</b></font></p>
<p begin="1440300000t" end="1491600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}誓要將你保護到底的決心已化作言語放聲吶喊</b></font></p>
<p begin="1494100000t" end="1541700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>巻き戻しの中　掴んだ愛は　そう</b></font></p>
<p begin="1494100000t" end="1541700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}回放逝去的倒帶  把對你永恆的摯愛捧在心中</b></font></p>
<p begin="1542900000t" end="1565000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>離しはしないから</b></font></p>
<p begin="1542900000t" end="1565000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}定不會輕易放手</b></font></p>
<p begin="1566700000t" end="1618000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>散りばめた想い　今一度きりの願いへ</b></font></p>
<p begin="1566700000t" end="1618000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}這是最後一次請求  將這散落一地的思念</b></font></p>
