<p begin="1619700000t" end="1667600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>次への僕に　託したよ</b></font></p>
<p begin="1619700000t" end="1667600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}託付給未來的自己</b></font></p>
<p begin="1668100000t" end="1718900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>いつかの約束　光の道しるべになる</b></font></p>
<p begin="1668100000t" end="1718900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}曾經的約定  化作黎明的燈塔指引我前進</b></font></p>
<p begin="1718900000t" end="1829500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>誓いをさあ　君のため　最期まで</b></font></p>
<p begin="1718900000t" end="1829500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}我發誓將為了你支撐到最後一刻</b></font></p>
<p begin="1831600000t" end="1880400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>涙さえ力に変えてきっと　描いていた望む未来へ</b></font></p>
<p begin="1831600000t" end="1880400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}連淚水也化作力量  一定會將心中描繪的所期待的未來</b></font></p>
<p begin="1882400000t" end="1907100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86"><font face="DFGHSGothic-W5" size="37"><b>繋ぐよ</b></font></p>
<p begin="1882400000t" end="1907100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87"><font face="方正兰亭中黑_GBK" size="42"><b>{\an8}與現實銜接</b></font></p>
<p begin="1960400000t" end="1984400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>讓我在這座宅邸工作吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="1998700000t" end="2044600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>想在羅茲瓦爾的宅邸支撐過一星期  有兩個必要的條件</b></font></p>
<p begin="2052500000t" end="2081300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>第一條是取得宅邸有關人員的信賴</b></font></p>
<p begin="2089700000t" end="2136100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>如果沒有通過他們的審視  就很有可能被殺人滅口</b></font></p>
<p begin="2152800000t" end="2200800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這不僅指雷姆和拉姆  還包含他們的主人羅茲瓦爾</b></font></p>
<p begin="2212500000t" end="2223800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>然後第二條</b></font></p>
<p begin="2229800000t" end="2251400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>就是把襲擊羅茲瓦爾宅邸的咒術師…</b></font></p>
<p begin="2263800000t" end="2269300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>給予擊破</b></font></p>
<p begin="2298200000t" end="2313500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>累壞了</b></font></p>
<p begin="2313500000t" end="2329400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>還真勤奮</b></font></p>
<p begin="2334900000t" end="2349600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>還沒結束呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="2351700000t" end="2368200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>還有晚飯的準備和房間打掃</b></font></p>
<p begin="2371700000t" end="2394400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>稍微休息一下後  就得回去工作</b></font></p>
<p begin="2395600000t" end="2415500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>第一天就幹勁十足呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="2417000000t" end="2428500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那是當然</b></font></p>
<p begin="2443900000t" end="2468600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>畢竟關係著很多重要的東西</b></font></p>
<p begin="2516900000t" end="2524100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>話說回來…</b></font></p>
<p begin="2534500000t" end="2562400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>愛蜜莉雅炭是適用什麼魔法的魔法使?</b></font></p>
<p begin="2565890000t" end="2593500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>嚴格來說莉雅不是魔法使</b></font></p>
<p begin="2596490000t" end="2613800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>與我的契約也是</b></font></p>
<p begin="2625600000t" end="2637800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>她是精靈使</b></font></p>
<p begin="2644100000t" end="2669500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>魔法使和精靈使是不一樣的啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="2674000000t" end="2708200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>魔法使是用自己體內的魔力來使用魔法</b></font></p>
<p begin="2713500000t" end="2753900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>反過來精靈使是用大氣中的魔力來使用法術</b></font></p>
<p begin="2756900000t" end="2779000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>所以這兩者有什麼區別呢  老師</b></font></p>
<p begin="2780100000t" end="2804100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>簡單地說就是會不會使用到生命門</b></font></p>
<p begin="2808500000t" end="2813500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>生命門?</b></font></p>
<p begin="2820500000t" end="2849900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>就是指在體內的魔力通過的門</b></font></p>
<p begin="2855100000t" end="2896600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>通過生命門來獲得魔力  再通過生命門來釋放魔力</b></font></p>
<p begin="2899600000t" end="2927600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>原來如此  就是指控制魔力值的水龍頭</b></font></p>
<p begin="2931300000t" end="2946300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>昴你也應該有的哦</b></font></p>
<p begin="2951400000t" end="2980600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真的嗎?  也就是說我也能使用魔法嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="2983600000t" end="3007000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>總之先調查一下昴的屬性吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="3013800000t" end="3059600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>在魔法裡有著火  水  風  土四種魔力屬性</b></font></p>
<p begin="3087300000t" end="3103600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>好有魔法的效果音</b></font></p>
<p begin="3106100000t" end="3122600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我知道了  昴的屬性</b></font></p>
<p begin="3123600000t" end="3135700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>來了  我就等此刻了</b></font></p>
<p begin="3140900000t" end="3152000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>果然是熱情的火?</b></font></p>
<p begin="3156100000t" end="3178300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>又或者是冷靜沉著並帥氣的水?</b></font></p>
<p begin="3184000000t" end="3203000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>亦或者是拂過草原清爽的風</b></font></p>
<p begin="3208100000t" end="3232300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>還是如穩重的大地般的可靠的土</b></font></p>
<p begin="3239000000t" end="3243800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是陰呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="3243800000t" end="3254200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>居然全部駁回!</b></font></p>
<p begin="3258400000t" end="3282900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>還真少見  居然是陰屬性</b></font></p>
<p begin="3287500000t" end="3316700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>話說陰是什麼  分類不是只有四個嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="3317100000t" end="3330800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>分類都出錯了</b></font></p>
<p begin="3333800000t" end="3372800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>四個基本屬性外  還有陰與陽的兩種屬性</b></font></p>
<p begin="3375400000t" end="3396100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>聽起來好像是非常厲害的能力</b></font></p>
<p begin="3399500000t" end="3420100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>比方是五千年一遇的天才這種</b></font></p>
<p begin="3424000000t" end="3441400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>要說陰屬性的魔法</b></font></p>
<p begin="3449100000t" end="3478100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>就是阻礙對手的視野  屏蔽聲音</b></font></p>
<p begin="3481100000t" end="3498400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>還有延緩別人的動作這類的吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="3500100000t" end="3510700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b><font size="32">Debuff</font></b></font></p>
<p begin="3500100000t" end="3510700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>「減益魔法」特化</b></font></p>
<p begin="3516200000t" end="3536600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>簡單來說就是遮幕之類的吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="3542300000t" end="3563700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>記得是障眼法類型的魔法呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="3581200000t" end="3594600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>稍微試一下吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="3596400000t" end="3612200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真的嗎?  讓我見識一下</b></font></p>
<p begin="3598600000t" end="3609000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="39"><b>{\an8}等下  帕克</b></font></p>
<p begin="3623500000t" end="3631300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>遮幕</b></font></p>
<p begin="3768500000t" end="3779600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>好了  結束</b></font></p>
<p begin="3796900000t" end="3815600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>怎麼樣  剛剛那個就是遮幕</b></font></p>
<p begin="3822800000t" end="3832500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你還好嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="3856300000t" end="3872600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>沒事</b></font></p>
<p begin="3873400000t" end="3895900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>雖然很不起眼  但是效果非常強</b></font></p>
<p begin="3900100000t" end="3925800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我也能使用那個叫遮幕的魔法吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="3927600000t" end="3944900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這取決於修行了</b></font></p>
<p begin="3950800000t" end="3965200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>要試試體驗入學嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="3969000000t" end="3981300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>拜託您了  師父</b></font></p>
<p begin="4001100000t" end="4031100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我來輔助  因為會使用到昴體內的魔力</b></font></p>
<p begin="4033900000t" end="4057400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>所以魔法本身是從昴的生命門裡出來的</b></font></p>
<p begin="4061700000t" end="4096000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>萬一昴的魔力暴走導致身體爆炸</b></font></p>
<p begin="4099000000t" end="4120900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>會弄髒莉雅的衣服  你就離遠一點吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="4131900000t" end="4164700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>會變成那樣的機率應該是超級低吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="4167200000t" end="4191100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>還能從容地說這些話  就說明你沒問題</b></font></p>
<p begin="4198500000t" end="4214100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那麼  想像一下</b></font></p>
<p begin="4220000000t" end="4238600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你體內的魔力的流動</b></font></p>
<p begin="4244300000t" end="4279300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>然後其中一部分從生命門中流出體外</b></font></p>
<p begin="4286000000t" end="4316200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>想像的話就交給本人吧  我可是很擅長腦洞的</b></font></p>
<p begin="4395700000t" end="4430400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真傷腦筋  生命門突然有些…</b></font></p>
<p begin="4499600000t" end="4536500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>從結果來說  因為昴的生命門很難控制</b></font></p>
<p begin="4536500000t" end="4550500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>所以還是不要勉強比較好</b></font></p>
<p begin="4554200000t" end="4576400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>說沒問題的不是你嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="4589600000t" end="4601800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>一點都不可愛</b></font></p>
<p begin="4603900000t" end="4639900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不管如何  是因為昴還不會控管生命門</b></font></p>
<p begin="4644500000t" end="4686700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>所以才會無視使用方的意志  從體內一下子噴了出來</b></font></p>
<p begin="4690300000t" end="4724300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我是沒蓋好瓶蓋的醬油嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="4736000000t" end="4746600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不可以亂動</b></font></p>
<p begin="4754000000t" end="4774300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>畢竟你身內的魔力都用光了</b></font></p>
<p begin="4781500000t" end="4802100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>看來今天可能沒辦法工作了</b></font></p>
<p begin="4802100000t" end="4811600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那可不行</b></font></p>
<p begin="4816300000t" end="4829100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你不可以勉強自己</b></font></p>
<p begin="4836500000t" end="4856000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>現在就算要勉強  也要堅持下去</b></font></p>
<p begin="4860700000t" end="4877100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>現在一天也不能浪費</b></font></p>
<p begin="4893000000t" end="4911500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真拿你沒辦法</b></font></p>
<p begin="4915400000t" end="4918900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真是的</b></font></p>
<p begin="4931500000t" end="4943600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你要做什麼</b></font></p>
<p begin="4958600000t" end="4962500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>咬一下</b></font></p>
<p begin="4966500000t" end="4969000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>嗯?</b></font></p>
<p begin="4976900000t" end="4998500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>咬一咬之後吞下去  來吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="5039500000t" end="5059000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>剛剛那是…</b></font></p>
<p begin="5072400000t" end="5089700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這是一種叫做波克果實的水果</b></font></p>
<p begin="5094200000t" end="5118500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>吃下去之後  身體中的魔力會活性化</b></font></p>
<p begin="5121100000t" end="5145490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>能讓生命門獲得一些力量</b></font></p>
<p begin="5165700000t" end="5191900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>抱歉  總覺得好像給你添麻煩了</b></font></p>
<p begin="5208090000t" end="5225900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>昴真是不懂</b></font></p>
<p begin="5241200000t" end="5258800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>比起說好幾次的抱歉</b></font></p>
<p begin="5262900000t" end="5296000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>說一次謝謝  會讓對方更加滿意</b></font></p>
<p begin="5307200000t" end="5321000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我不是要你道歉</b></font></p>
<p begin="5325400000t" end="5342500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是因為想幫你才做的</b></font></p>
<p begin="5350600000t" end="5355100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>知道嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="5400000000t" end="5431700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>然後拉姆  在你看來</b></font></p>
<p begin="5433400000t" end="5455200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你對他的評價是如何</b></font></p>
<p begin="5465600000t" end="5490700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>從能力上說  可以算是無能</b></font></p>
<p begin="5495000000t" end="5518500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不過在重要的地方又有些過於機靈</b></font></p>
<p begin="5527500000t" end="5555800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我覺得還需要觀察一陣子</b></font></p>
<p begin="5563200000t" end="5601200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這件事需要非常慎重地處理</b></font></p>
<p begin="5609000000t" end="5632100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>請身為姐姐的你要好好注意</b></font></p>
<p begin="5635800000t" end="5663800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>別讓雷姆過於衝動</b></font></p>
<p begin="5683200000t" end="5706800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>第一天的表現還算過得去吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="5711600000t" end="5749600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>應該贏得不少雷姆和拉姆的信賴</b></font></p>
<p begin="5756800000t" end="5779500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>但是問題果然還是在於咒術師的襲擊嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="5782600000t" end="5796900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>該如何與之對抗才好</b></font></p>
<p begin="5824300000t" end="5847600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>想知道咒術師更多的情報?</b></font></p>
<p begin="5850000000t" end="5878300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>沒錯  要如何才能防止詛咒?</b></font></p>
<p begin="5884600000t" end="5900200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>沒辦法</b></font></p>
<p begin="5903100000t" end="5906100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>什麼?</b></font></p>
<p begin="5912400000t" end="5950200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>咒術一旦發動  就沒有可解之法</b></font></p>
<p begin="5956500000t" end="5984300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>一旦發動就回天無力  這就是咒術</b></font></p>
<p begin="5992700000t" end="6019800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>居然能把即死抗性給無效化  也太強大了</b></font></p>
<p begin="6024600000t" end="6061700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不過發動之前的咒術  就只是單純的術式</b></font></p>
<p begin="6063600000t" end="6082500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>對碧蒂而言  要解除就是小菜一碟</b></font></p>
<p begin="6112300000t" end="6123400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>魔女遺留的氣味</b></font></p>
<p begin="6130400000t" end="6153900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>說起來  雷姆也這麼說過</b></font></p>
<p begin="6157800000t" end="6169000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>魔女是什麼</b></font></p>
<p begin="6176600000t" end="6197600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>難道說是咒術師的夥伴嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="6224000000t" end="6268000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>在這世上能代表「魔女」這詞的僅有一個存在</b></font></p>
<p begin="6290000000t" end="6302500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>嫉妒魔女嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="6305700000t" end="6332700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>就是她  嫉妒魔女莎緹拉</b></font></p>
<p begin="6337500000t" end="6377900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>曾經把冠有大罪之名的六位魔女全部都吞噬掉</b></font></p>
<p begin="6380000000t" end="6416300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>併吞下半個世界的最惡劣的災難</b></font></p>
<p begin="6425900000t" end="6449500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>有人說  她渴望愛</b></font></p>
<p begin="6455700000t" end="6483200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>有人說  她不懂人言</b></font></p>
<p begin="6488300000t" end="6532600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>有人說  她的身軀永不腐朽衰敗  永恆的存在</b></font></p>
<p begin="6539000000t" end="6580600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>有人說  就算以龍與英雄以及賢者的力量將其封印</b></font></p>
<p begin="6582900000t" end="6601800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>也無法消滅她的身軀</b></font></p>
<p begin="6608800000t" end="6650900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>有人說  她的真身是銀髮半妖精</b></font></p>
<p begin="6686000000t" end="6706500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我是  莎緹拉</b></font></p>
<p begin="6727100000t" end="6757900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>在什麼時候才會假冒嫉妒魔女之名呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="6761500000t" end="6786100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不  說是假冒也不好</b></font></p>
<p begin="6792100000t" end="6825200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>改成借用嫉妒魔女之名比較好吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="6830400000t" end="6854100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不管怎麼說  這都是不要命的舉動</b></font></p>
<p begin="6860300000t" end="6897200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>居然假冒魔女之名  我只能說那個人頭腦有問題</b></font></p>
<p begin="6946100000t" end="6966000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這樣啊  所以才…</b></font></p>
<p begin="6977500000t" end="6997900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>如果是故意裝成奇怪的傢伙  讓別人避而遠之</b></font></p>
<p begin="7001100000t" end="7029900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>就不會讓別人捲進王選的紛爭之中</b></font></p>
<p begin="7035000000t" end="7047000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你在說什麼</b></font></p>
<p begin="7072800000t" end="7084000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>沒什麼</b></font></p>
<p begin="7103000000t" end="7118900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>Good Morning</b></font></p>
<p begin="7121100000t" end="7143900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>今天也是非常適合曬衣服的大晴天</b></font></p>
<p begin="7146100000t" end="7165000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>一起來度過Happiness的一天吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="7167300000t" end="7193000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>好  Victory</b></font></p>
<p begin="7210900000t" end="7232700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="39"><b>{\an8}Victory!</b></font></p>
<p begin="7223700000t" end="7246300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>今天也是從早上開始就精神飽滿</b></font></p>
<p begin="7255200000t" end="7290900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>今天除了接受女僕姐妹的教訓和差遣的同時</b></font></p>
<p begin="7291700000t" end="7310900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>也要充分享受傭人的生活</b></font></p>
<p begin="7312100000t" end="7332700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>但是如果我在這種生活感到疲憊不堪了</b></font></p>
<p begin="7334000000t" end="7353900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>說不定會飛到愛蜜莉雅炭的膝蓋上</b></font></p>
<p begin="7354300000t" end="7366300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>所以要記得幫我預留位置</b></font></p>
<p begin="7368900000t" end="7394500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>看你洗臉的樣子  還真像貓啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="7396700000t" end="7429800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>精靈果然也會犯睏  也還是會睡過頭嗎?</b></font></p>
<p begin="7439800000t" end="7468900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你們如果過於疲憊也會犯睏吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="7475500000t" end="7507000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>精靈也是  只要作為行動之源的魔力減少的話</b></font></p>
<p begin="7513100000t" end="7540100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>也會出現類似的情況</b></font></p>
<p begin="7545100000t" end="7562900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你們兩個竟然一起熬夜</b></font></p>
<p begin="7565200000t" end="7594100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>反正是在討論喜歡的人的話題  一直熱聊到深夜吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="7596300000t" end="7608600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>也算我一份吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="7620400000t" end="7631200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>問我喜歡的人?</b></font></p>
<p begin="7631200000t" end="7647500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那個雖然很害羞  但是…</b></font></p>
<p begin="7647500000t" end="7679000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我喜歡的是帕克  而帕克喜歡的是我</b></font></p>
<p begin="7683500000t" end="7695700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>好  話題結束了</b></font></p>
<p begin="7697400000t" end="7722200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>相親相愛!?  我的介入餘地呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="7724400000t" end="7733700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>當然沒有</b></font></p>
<p begin="7736500000t" end="7756900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>莉雅可是被我迷得神魂顛倒</b></font></p>
<p begin="7763500000t" end="7803500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>雖然昴也不差  不過和我比起來就差遠了</b></font></p>
<p begin="7807800000t" end="7826700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>還是老實放棄莉雅…</b></font></p>
<p begin="7836600000t" end="7853500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>兩位不要太得寸進尺了!</b></font></p>
<p begin="7857500000t" end="7880100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>太過火的話  我也是會生氣的</b></font></p>
<p begin="7881800000t" end="7903100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>好痛好痛  生氣了生氣了</b></font></p>
<p begin="7918700000t" end="7943500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>差不多該走了  不然女僕姐妹可是會發火的</b></font></p>
<p begin="7946500000t" end="7951900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那麼再見了</b></font></p>
<p begin="7986800000t" end="8009200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你怎麼了  一臉無法釋懷的樣子</b></font></p>
<p begin="8024700000t" end="8074100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>總覺得心裡有些煩悶  我也不太會形容</b></font></p>
<p begin="8084800000t" end="8108700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>莉雅會感到困惑  也是在所難免</b></font></p>
<p begin="8112600000t" end="8136300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>畢竟事態變得有點傷腦筋了</b></font></p>
<p begin="8153300000t" end="8171600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>Don't mind  Don't mind  別在意</b></font></p>
<p begin="8173900000t" end="8180700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>沒問題</b></font></p>
<p begin="8185300000t" end="8194300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>傷腦筋?</b></font></p>
