<p begin="11202700000t" end="11239300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我努力了  拚命努力過了</b></font></p>
<p begin="11244000000t" end="11267100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>非常拚命  拚命做了各種嘗試</b></font></p>
<p begin="11256800000t" end="11392900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}大きなこの羽が  ぼうやは見えないのね</b></font></p>
<p begin="11256800000t" end="11392900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}小男孩是看不見這雙巨翼吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="11275300000t" end="11301300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>努力嘗試讓一切變好</b></font></p>
<p begin="11308700000t" end="11374100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真的  真的從未如此努力過</b></font></p>
<p begin="11374500000t" end="11393100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>嗯  我知道</b></font></p>
<p begin="11392900000t" end="11521700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}なにも知らない  まあるいほっぺよ</b></font></p>
<p begin="11392900000t" end="11521700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}那一臉對世事無知的嘟嘟圓臉</b></font></p>
<p begin="11411500000t" end="11434800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我喜歡這裡</b></font></p>
<p begin="11444200000t" end="11477500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我很珍視這裡</b></font></p>
<p begin="11484400000t" end="11521300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>所以  我才拚命想要把它奪回來</b></font></p>
<p begin="11529200000t" end="11664400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}ねむれやねむれ しずかな水辺においで</b></font></p>
<p begin="11529200000t" end="11664400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}在寂靜的水邊好好地休息睡覺吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="11530000000t" end="11560400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>好害怕  我好害怕</b></font></p>
<p begin="11569800000t" end="11591000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我害怕再次被人投以那種眼神</b></font></p>
<p begin="11595900000t" end="11655700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我好討厭這樣想的自己  不想要這樣</b></font></p>
<p begin="11664400000t" end="11732400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}ぼうやの夢は</b></font></p>
<p begin="11664400000t" end="11732400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}在小男孩的夢中</b></font></p>
<p begin="11731900000t" end="11740500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>昴</b></font></p>
<p begin="11732400000t" end="11865300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}竜の背に運ばれて  山の向こうへ消える</b></font></p>
<p begin="11732400000t" end="11865300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}夢見自己坐在龍背上雲遊  並在山的另一側隱去</b></font></p>
<p begin="11751000000t" end="11760400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>噓</b></font></p>
<p begin="11772200000t" end="11791200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>昴  只是睡著了嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="11798300000t" end="11801900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>沒錯</b></font></p>
<p begin="11821600000t" end="11839900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>看  他跟小孩一樣吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="11848900000t" end="11882600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>看來昴今天沒法再工作了呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="11893000000t" end="11916500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是啊  今天就讓他休息吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="11925300000t" end="11963100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>工作才第二天就休息  真是個壞孩子</b></font></p>
<p begin="11972300000t" end="11995500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>等他恢復了  記得懲罰他</b></font></p>
<p begin="12007100000t" end="12032500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這樣看著他  都沒心思懲罰他了</b></font></p>
<p begin="12039000000t" end="12169400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}竜の背に運ばれて  山の向こうへ消える</b></font></p>
<p begin="12039000000t" end="12169400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}夢見自己坐在龍背上雲遊  並在山的另一側隱去</b></font></p>
<p begin="12053900000t" end="12058200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>嗯</b></font></p>
<p begin="12102200000t" end="12134900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我去告訴姐姐  昴今天派不上用場</b></font></p>
<p begin="12143700000t" end="12147700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>雷姆</b></font></p>
<p begin="12163600000t" end="12177000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>昴是個乖孩子</b></font></p>
<p begin="12278800000t" end="12305700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>在喜歡的女生面前放聲大哭</b></font></p>
<p begin="12308000000t" end="12339300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>最後還帶著滿臉鼻涕眼淚睡過去了</b></font></p>
<p begin="12342400000t" end="12360800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這算是哪門子的羞恥Play</b></font></p>
<p begin="12360800000t" end="12376700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不行  我沒救了</b></font></p>
<p begin="12380300000t" end="12410400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你半夜三更跑進來就要跟我說這些嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="12415100000t" end="12430800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>別這麼說  碧翠子</b></font></p>
<p begin="12430800000t" end="12449800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>畢竟我們關係那麼好</b></font></p>
<p begin="12449800000t" end="12471000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>碧蒂和你有什麼關係嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="12479100000t" end="12504000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>慢著  你剛叫我什麼</b></font></p>
<p begin="12506800000t" end="12520900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你說碧翠子啊</b></font></p>
<p begin="12526900000t" end="12559500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我認為要表現親近感  愛稱是必不可少的</b></font></p>
<p begin="12564700000t" end="12584800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>所以我以後就叫你碧翠子了</b></font></p>
<p begin="12589700000t" end="12617400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這是我對你能盡到的最大程度的親近的證明</b></font></p>
<p begin="12619500000t" end="12640100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你那強加於人的善意是怎麼回事</b></font></p>
<p begin="12644400000t" end="12669600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>何止讓人噁心  簡直讓人想吐</b></font></p>
<p begin="12671400000t" end="12696000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>別這麼冷淡  碧翠子</b></font></p>
<p begin="12704700000t" end="12712600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>實際上…</b></font></p>
<p begin="12733300000t" end="12754600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我已經被逼到死路上了</b></font></p>
<p begin="12757000000t" end="12780400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>老實說關於詛咒的事  希望你能幫我</b></font></p>
<p begin="12784200000t" end="12814200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我應該說過  咒術一旦發動就無法解除</b></font></p>
<p begin="12816100000t" end="12829200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你確實說過</b></font></p>
<p begin="12831700000t" end="12869900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不過在詛咒發動前  能查出術式嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="12871500000t" end="12906000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle446"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>如果是還沒發動的術式  我是可以找出來</b></font></p>
<p begin="12930900000t" end="12946300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle447"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>詛咒是如何釋放到人身上的</b></font></p>
<p begin="12957100000t" end="12990700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle448"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>咒術有一個絕對不能違背的規則</b></font></p>
<p begin="12997600000t" end="13009900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle449"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不能違背的規則?</b></font></p>
<p begin="13024500000t" end="13068800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle450"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>接觸施咒對象  這是必要條件</b></font></p>
<p begin="13083600000t" end="13100900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle451"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>要說接觸到誰…</b></font></p>
<p begin="13105300000t" end="13130300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle452"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>除了宅邸裡的人  就只剩山腳下的村子了</b></font></p>
<p begin="13140800000t" end="13175500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle453"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>也就是我在村裡被人下了咒術  當晚咒術發動</b></font></p>
<p begin="13177600000t" end="13192800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle454"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>最後致死亡的情況嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="13205000000t" end="13238800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle455"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這樣來說上次咒術師對雷姆下手也能說得通了</b></font></p>
<p begin="13245700000t" end="13279000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle456"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>因為我沒去村裡  所以對方把目標轉向了雷姆</b></font></p>
<p begin="13289800000t" end="13314900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle457"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>連起來了  所有的事情都連起來了</b></font></p>
<p begin="13321900000t" end="13338700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle458"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>終於讓我抓到線索了</b></font></p>
<p begin="13341700000t" end="13356800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle459"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>可惡!</b></font></p>
<p begin="13364300000t" end="13398400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle460"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這就是你求人的態度嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="13403500000t" end="13436400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle461"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>既然剛才的話有幫助  你不覺得該說點什麼嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="13441500000t" end="13455000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle462"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>嗯  沒錯</b></font></p>
<p begin="13461600000t" end="13469100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle463"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你幫大忙了</b></font></p>
<p begin="13469700000t" end="13491300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle464"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>多虧你讓我看到了光明</b></font></p>
<p begin="13494800000t" end="13521300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle465"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>碧翠子  我愛你</b></font></p>
<p begin="13505300000t" end="13510100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle466"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="39"><b>{\an8}放手…</b></font></p>
<p begin="13525400000t" end="13536800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle467"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>放我下來!</b></font></p>
<p begin="13561500000t" end="13602800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle468"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="35">{\an8}本字幕由動漫國字幕組製作(dmguo.org)<br />僅供試看,請支持購買正版音像製品</font></p>
<p begin="13603900000t" end="13621200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle469"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>總之  雖然發生了不少事</b></font></p>
<p begin="13613200000t" end="13651200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle470"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="35">{\an8}翻譯:Ino17&小勳&我不是小呆   校對:初夏   時軸:秋穗姬   後期&MKV:小聖   特效:鎖定</font></p>
<p begin="13621200000t" end="13645000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle471"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不過今天就要轉換心情  煥發新面貌</b></font></p>
<p begin="13645000000t" end="13655700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle472"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是膝枕吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="13659300000t" end="13669600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle473"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是膝枕呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="13689100000t" end="13706200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle474"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>難道你們都知道了?</b></font></p>
<p begin="13715700000t" end="13728300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle475"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>昴  早</b></font></p>
<p begin="13730200000t" end="13751900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle476"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}Oh,please don't let me die</b></font></p>
<p begin="13730200000t" end="13751900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle477"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}請不要讓我離開</b></font></p>
<p begin="13730200000t" end="13740100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle478"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>愛蜜莉雅炭</b></font></p>
<p begin="13752700000t" end="13774400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle479"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}Waiting for your touch</b></font></p>
<p begin="13752700000t" end="13774400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle480"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}你的觸碰  我的等待</b></font></p>
<p begin="13754300000t" end="13785200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle481"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那個  總覺得有點害羞呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="13807200000t" end="13823100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle482"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你身體什麼的都沒事了嗎</b></font></p>
<p begin="13808600000t" end="13829500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle483"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}No,don't give up on life</b></font></p>
<p begin="13808600000t" end="13829500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle484"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}不  請不要對生命無愛</b></font></p>
<p begin="13825400000t" end="13854100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle485"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>雖然在聽到愛蜜莉雅炭的聲音前  還有點危險</b></font></p>
<p begin="13830700000t" end="13849900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle486"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}This endless dead end</b></font></p>
<p begin="13830700000t" end="13849900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle487"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}儘管這絕望  不竭不衰</b></font></p>
<p begin="13888600000t" end="13900700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle488"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我已經沒事了</b></font></p>
<p begin="13906700000t" end="13922800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle489"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那個  怎麼說呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="13907900000t" end="13947100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle490"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}狂った時計　刻む命</b></font></p>
<p begin="13907900000t" end="13947100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle491"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}失準的時鐘  記錄著生命</b></font></p>
<p begin="13931300000t" end="13941500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle492"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>感覺有很多方面都抱…</b></font></p>
<p begin="13947900000t" end="13985900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle493"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}こぼれてく記憶の砂</b></font></p>
<p begin="13947900000t" end="13985900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle494"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}散落滿地的記憶之砂</b></font></p>
<p begin="13969300000t" end="13991900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle495"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不  感謝你為我做的一切</b></font></p>
<p begin="13986700000t" end="14024700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle496"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}芽生えた想いまで</b></font></p>
<p begin="13986700000t" end="14024700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle497"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}以及萌生的思念</b></font></p>
<p begin="14013000000t" end="14040100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle498"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>沒事  不客氣</b></font></p>
<p begin="14025500000t" end="14074300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle499"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}ねえ　こんなに呆気なく</b></font></p>
<p begin="14025500000t" end="14074300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle500"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}你看  卻是那麼輕易</b></font></p>
<p begin="14055200000t" end="14084700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle501"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那麼昴  該準備開始早晨的工作吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="14086900000t" end="14107700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle502"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>要開始早晨的任務了</b></font></p>
<p begin="14093900000t" end="14147300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle503"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}消えてしまうの</b></font></p>
<p begin="14093900000t" end="14147300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle504"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}消失殆盡</b></font></p>
<p begin="14116000000t" end="14148900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle505"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>在此之前  我有個請求</b></font></p>
<p begin="14147300000t" end="14159800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle506"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}I wish I was there</b></font></p>
<p begin="14147300000t" end="14159800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle507"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}我希望能與你同在</b></font></p>
<p begin="14149600000t" end="14159700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle508"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>是膝枕吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="14159700000t" end="14168900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle509"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>肯定是膝枕</b></font></p>
<p begin="14160200000t" end="14180300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle510"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}Oh,please don't let me die</b></font></p>
<p begin="14160200000t" end="14180300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle511"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}請不要讓我離開</b></font></p>
<p begin="14168900000t" end="14184900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle512"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>才不是那麼沒節操的請求!</b></font></p>
<p begin="14181100000t" end="14201100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle513"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}Waiting for your touch</b></font></p>
<p begin="14181100000t" end="14201100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle514"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}你的觸碰  我的等待</b></font></p>
<p begin="14189300000t" end="14206500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle515"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>實際上我想去一趟村裡</b></font></p>
<p begin="14202800000t" end="14246200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle516"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}二度となにも失くさぬように</b></font></p>
<p begin="14202800000t" end="14246200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle517"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}為了不再失去曾經擁有的寶物</b></font></p>
<p begin="14209400000t" end="14220300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle518"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>就在這附近吧</b></font></p>
<p begin="14227600000t" end="14245500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle519"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>有沒有外出採購之類的預定呢</b></font></p>
<p begin="14247000000t" end="14314100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle520"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}私を忘れて　始めて　Restart</b></font></p>
<p begin="14247000000t" end="14314100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle521"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}讓我忘卻自己的過去  重新開始旅途</b></font></p>
<p begin="14254200000t" end="14278000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle522"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>香料確實有些不夠了</b></font></p>
<p begin="14280500000t" end="14305900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle523"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>我打算明天去一趟村裡</b></font></p>
<p begin="14307300000t" end="14328300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle524"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>那就改變下預定  今天去如何</b></font></p>
<p begin="14315000000t" end="14336200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle525"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}No,don't give up on life</b></font></p>
<p begin="14315000000t" end="14336200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle526"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}不  請不要對生命無愛</b></font></p>
<p begin="14330900000t" end="14353200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle527"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>既然快用完了  那肯定是快點採購回來比較好</b></font></p>
<p begin="14338300000t" end="14357100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle528"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}This endless dead end</b></font></p>
<p begin="14338300000t" end="14357100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle529"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}儘管這絕望  不竭不衰</b></font></p>
<p begin="14359200000t" end="14401700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle530"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}君を砕くこの悲しみが</b></font></p>
<p begin="14359200000t" end="14401700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle531"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}願那讓你苦不堪言的悲傷</b></font></p>
<p begin="14382800000t" end="14395200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle532"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>這點小事  沒什麼不好的</b></font></p>
<p begin="14401000000t" end="14407900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle533"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>姐姐…</b></font></p>
<p begin="14405900000t" end="14457200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle534"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}いつか終わりますように</b></font></p>
<p begin="14405900000t" end="14457200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle535"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}會迎來完結的一天</b></font></p>
<p begin="14411900000t" end="14430400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle536"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>反正遲早要去採購</b></font></p>
<p begin="14431400000t" end="14441500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle537"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>現在也沒什麼要緊的事</b></font></p>
<p begin="14446200000t" end="14466600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle538"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>而且還有巴魯斯負責拿東西</b></font></p>
<p begin="14457600000t" end="14493500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle539"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}For now I'll see you off</b></font></p>
<p begin="14457600000t" end="14493500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle540"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}而我卻要目送你離開</b></font></p>
<p begin="14478200000t" end="14494300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle541"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>既然姐姐都這麼說了</b></font></p>
<p begin="14496300000t" end="14507400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle542"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>太好了</b></font></p>
<p begin="14513900000t" end="14527700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle543"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}And we'll die</b></font></p>
<p begin="14513900000t" end="14527700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle544"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}我們終將會重來</b></font></p>
<p begin="14515500000t" end="14535400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle545"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>不過  拉姆也要一起去</b></font></p>
<p begin="14528500000t" end="14548500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle546"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}Waiting for a new day</b></font></p>
<p begin="14528500000t" end="14548500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle547"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}重來對新一天的期待</b></font></p>
<p begin="14542400000t" end="14561500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle548"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>你真是被群花擁簇啊  巴魯斯</b></font></p>
<p begin="14549400000t" end="14559400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle549"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}二度と</b></font></p>
<p begin="14549400000t" end="14559400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle550"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}再一次的期待</b></font></p>
<p begin="14577200000t" end="14611100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle551"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="50"><b>真希望那些花不帶毒…</b></font></p>
<p begin="14591900000t" end="14603600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle552"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}And we'll die</b></font></p>
<p begin="14591900000t" end="14603600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle553"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}我們終將會重來</b></font></p>
<p begin="14605700000t" end="14624900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle554"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}Waiting for a new day</b></font></p>
<p begin="14605700000t" end="14624900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle555"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}重來對新一天的期待</b></font></p>
<p begin="14620100000t" end="14652300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle556"><font face="方正兰亭粗黑_GBK" size="70" color="#a098ce"><b><font color="#ffffff">哭過喊過  便不再哭<font color="#abacba">泣</font></font></b></font></p>
<p begin="14627000000t" end="14637800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle557"><font face="Reishoreiryu" size="36"><b>{\an9}君と</b></font></p>
<p begin="14627000000t" end="14637800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle558"><font face="方正隶变_GBK" size="40"><b>{\an9}與你攜手邁進</b></font></p>
